Package: chartdownloader
Architecture: any
Section: misc
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Simple Chart Downloader
 Download airport aeronautical charts including airport diagrams,
 minimums, Standard Instrument Departure (SID), Standard Terminal Arrival (STAR), and
 Instrument Approach (IAP) charts in PDF format.
 Supports conversion to PNG for use in Aerobask airplanes in XPlane. 

Package: chartdownloader-dbg
Architecture: any
Section: debug
Priority: extra
Depends: chartdownloader (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: debug information for chartdownloader
 This package contains debugging files used to investigate problems with the
 chartdownloader.
